<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Fan Meeting Project</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }

    .header .nav {
      position: absolute;
      top: 10px;
      right: 20px;
    }

    .header .nav a {
      color: white;
      margin: 0 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .content {
      margin-top: 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      width: 150px;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px;
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="nav">
      <a href="#">Home</a>
      <a href="#">로그인</a>
      <a href="#">회원가입</a>
    </div>
    <h1>환영합니다!</h1>
    <p>당신이 이 사이트에 들어온 이상 웹 서버를 완성할 때 까지 절대 나갈 수 없습니다!</p>
    <button>변우석 팬미팅 하기</button>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <div class="card">팬미팅 장소<br>그분 집 앞</div>
    <div class="card">팬미팅 시간<br>24시간</div>
    <div class="card">팬미팅 티켓 예매<br>알아봐</div>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    © 2024 클라우드 엔지니어 양성 과정 1기생 Mini Project 4팀. 모든 권리 보유.
  </div>
</body>

</html>